@node HISTORY "History"

  @{b}History@{ub}

  v1.1 (03.06.2001)
	 ˇ Now compiled with StormC 4
	 ˇ Enabled import of text-anchored images
	 ˇ German typographical closing quotes were still wrong

  v1.0 (28.12.2000)
    After no problems with AmigaWriter documents were reported, I raise the
    version number to 1.0 and upload it to Aminet as announced.

    Changes from v0.9:
    ˇ The filter does not require an FPU any longer
	 ˇ German typographical closing quotes were wrong
    ˇ For all greyscale values, the "K" value in the Pagestream CMYK model
      is set. Previously, this had only been done for black
    ˇ Some minor internal code revisions

  v0.9 (01.11.2000)
    Initial release only available from my homepage.

  @{" Main Page " link MAIN}

@endnode

